Wose wawo walongeligwa vinogile kwa ichimu cha uhuwilo wawo, mbali habule hata imwe wawo yoyahokele chiya choyawalaganile Mulungu.
Kwaviya Mulungu kakala kachilongela chochose chinogile ng'hani kwa ichimu chetu, muladi wanhu wawo sekewakamilike bila cheye.
Ivo kwaviya wingu kulu fana dino da wakalangama dodisang'hanila kwima habehi na cheye, leka chila chinhu chochidaha kuileka kutali na uhasanyi wowochizingiliza chihole chifose-fose, na chiitowe ng'hani na ugima wa ugima wochiwikigwe na Mulungu.
